Module ZiqiYang

Package org.ziqi.model

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Crate
    Crate class as GameObject, possessing CrateStatus enumeration.
    Diamond
    Diamond class as GameObject.
    Floor
    Floor class as GameObject.
    Layer
    Layer class as to store grids(2-d array) of GameObjects with the same type into one layer.
    Level
    Level class represents a game level and contains all information for that game level.
    Player
    Player class as GameObject, possessing PlayerDirection and PlayerStatus enumeration.
    ScoreRecord
    ScoreRecord class as to store information of high scores of each level.
    Wall
    Wall class as GameObject, possessing WallStatus enumeration.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description

    CrateStatus enumeration defines all status of Crate object.
    Player.PlayerDirection
    PlayerDirection enumeration defines all facing direction of Player object.
    Player.PlayerStatus
    PlayerStatus enumeration defines all status of Player object.
    Wall.WallStatus
    WallStatus enumeration defines all status of Wall object.
